dd459f59-3cf9-4b70-8147-1f1c95169724.title: <player>
dd459f59-3cf9-4b70-8147-1f1c95169724.text: Hi, I hear a woman called Elena is staying here.

84ded2a1-6ce7-47f0-ace0-9b3aa72436ae.title: Martha Rehnison
84ded2a1-6ce7-47f0-ace0-9b3aa72436ae.text:
Yes she was staying here, but slightly over a week ago
she was getting ready to go back. However she never
managed to leave.

c9224169-5ba2-4cc0-8e7d-e3edddbd8994.title: Martha Rehnison
c9224169-5ba2-4cc0-8e7d-e3edddbd8994.text:
My daughter Milli was playing near the west wall when
she saw some shadowy figures jump out and grab her.
Milli is upstairs if you wish to speak to her.

85f49aea-c771-4527-9bf9-adf401035d1b.title: Martha Rehnison
85f49aea-c771-4527-9bf9-adf401035d1b.text: I wish you luck, she did a lot for us.

cf778712-d4eb-47b8-b4e3-8213748708c4.title: <player>
cf778712-d4eb-47b8-b4e3-8213748708c4.text: Yes, she is safe at home now.

5e54b756-2fde-415e-860c-0c4cdfd96aed.title: Martha Rehnison
5e54b756-2fde-415e-860c-0c4cdfd96aed.text: That's good to hear, she helped us a lot.
